      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 116,
      "message": "I had intended to refactor this and will do so now. One point though: I would advise against using \"list\" in variable names as the underlying data structure can change without a corresponding change to the variable name which could lead to confusion down the line if someone expects it to be a list and it is, for example, a map.",
